subject: Hello and greetings
body:
Hello and greetings
.long time, hope you and your family and business all good
Just want to let you know, we have new production of goods now at more cheaper cost
So if you are still interested in buying the mask respirators, do let us know so we give you new quotations
Bet 
Dr Sally

subject: Re:     Hello and greetings
body:
Hello Dr. Sally,

Thank you for reaching out and I hope you're doing well too! It's great to hear about the new production of goods. I'm always interested in finding good deals.

Could you please provide more details about these masks? Like what type are they, how many layers do they have, and what materials are used in their production? Also, could you share some information about the manufacturing process?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon!

Best wishes,
Patrick
